languages.text: "Я решила, что надежнее будет доставить все сюда. Передай я все это Данроку, и он подвергся бы чудовищным соблазнам алчности. А ваш фактотум не выглядит как человек, умеющий сопротивляться соблазнам".

"I thought the safest thing would be to bring them all here. If I had handed them to Danrok, it would have been a monstrous temptation. And your avaricious Factotum does not strike me as someone who is good at resisting temptation."

languages.text: “我认为最安全的做法，就是把这些东西都带到你这里来。如果把这些财富交给丹罗克，对他而言恐怕会是个巨大的诱惑。而在我看来，你那位贪婪的高阶顾问并不擅长抵抗诱惑。”

traits.speaker: JaeCompanion

languages.text: 「一番安全なのは、全員をここに連れてくることだと思った。ダンロックに渡していたら、とんでもない誘惑に駆られていただろう。それに、あんたの貪欲なファクトタムは、誘惑に耐えるのが得意な人物とは思えないからね」
languages.original_text: "I thought the safest thing would be to bring them all here. If I had handed them to Danrok, it would have been a monstrous temptation. And your avaricious Factotum does not strike me as someone who is good at resisting temptation."

traits.speaker: JaeCompanion

languages.text: «Pensé que lo más seguro era traerlos todos aquí. Si se los hubiera dado a Danrok, la tentación habría sido monstruosa. Y su avaricioso factótum no me parece alguien muy proclive a resistir tentaciones».
languages.original_text: "I thought the safest thing would be to bring them all here. If I had handed them to Danrok, it would have been a monstrous temptation. And your avaricious Factotum does not strike me as someone who is good at resisting temptation."

languages.text: « Je me suis dit qu'il valait mieux tous les rassembler ici. Si je les avais donnés à Danrok, la tentation aurait été trop grande et je n'ai pas l'impression que votre factotum cupide est capable d'y résister. »

languages.text: "Ich hatte das Gefühl, es wäre am sichersten, wenn ich alles hierherbringen würde. Hätte ich sie Danrok gegeben, wäre das für ihn eine zu große Versuchung gewesen. Und Euer habgieriges Faktotum erscheint mir nicht wie jemand, der gut Versuchungen widerstehen kann."

languages.text: "En güvenli şeyin onları buraya getirmek olacağını düşündüm. Bunları Danrok'a verseydim bu, fazlasıyla baştan çıkarıcı bir fırsat olurdu. Senin paragöz Kâhyan da bana baştan çıkarıcılığa direnmede pek başarılıymış gibi görünmedi."
